<subSubSection pageId="70" pageNumber="71" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="70.[189,454,1029,1055]" box="[189,454,1029,1055]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,454,1029,1055]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,454,1029,1055]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Differential diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="70.[189,1399,1076,1244]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">
The new species belongs to the nominal subgenus (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1822" box="[823,938,1076,1102]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" sensu="stricto">
<emphasis box="[823,938,1076,1102]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Cheilosia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[948,1016,1076,1103]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" sensu="stricto">s. str.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), where it is close to 
<taxonomicName authority="Hellen, 1930" authorityName="Hellen" authorityYear="1930" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albohirta" subGenus="Cheilosia">
<emphasis box="[1284,1399,1076,1102]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Cheilosia</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[199,312,1111,1137]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Cheilosia</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis box="[331,441,1111,1137]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">albohirta</emphasis>
Hellén, 1930
</taxonomicName>
, from which it differs as follows: frons shiny, with stripes of grey pollinosity adjacent to eye, basoflagellomere orange, with dark antero-dorsal margin, pleura with some black pile and long black bristles. In 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hellen" authorityYear="1930" box="[627,771,1182,1208]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albohirta">
<emphasis box="[627,771,1182,1208]" italics="true" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">C. albohirta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the frons is densely grey pollinose, basoflagellomere black with reddish postero-ventral corner and pleura only whitish pilose.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption box="[189,1083,1998,2025]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71" startId="70.[189,232,1998,2024]" targetBox="[189,1398,1314,1960]" targetPageId="70">
<paragraph blockId="70.[189,1083,1998,2025]" box="[189,1083,1998,2025]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,282,1998,2024]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Fig. 38.</emphasis>
